<h3 id="sound-installation">Sound installation</h3>

<p>I am working on my first sound installation piece for an interactive exhibit at The Phoenix in Waterbury, VT. And I am highly jazzed about it. The exhibit will be a community created collage, for which I am designing an audio-reactive musical system which will take shape as the collage mural takes shape over the course of two days. Will do a little write-up on how it all works once I figure that out.</p>

<p>The sound installation will culminate with a performance consisting of me reacting and responding to the musical system on July 13 at 7pm.</p>
